high_descs: Turn around and go across the kitchen to the large sink on the right.
Pick up the egg in the back of the sink, behind the potato.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator ahead, to your right.
Place the egg on the second shelf of the refrigerator, wait a moment for it to chill, then remove the egg from the refrigerator.
Turn to your right and go to the microwave above the sink.
Place the egg in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold egg in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink
Pick up the egg that is sitting in the sink on the right, behind the potato
Turn around and walk to the fridge on your right
Open the fridge and place the egg on the second shelf to the left of the lettuce and apple then close the fridge. Then open the fridge and pick up the egg then shut the door
Turn to the right and walk to the sink
Open the microwave that is above the sink and place the egg on the right side of the plate inside then close the door
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled egg in a microwave

high_descs: Turn right and walk up to the fridge, then turn right and walk over to the sink.
Pick up the egg out of the sink.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the egg inside on the top shelf then close the fridge, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and take out the now chilled egg, then close the fridge.
Turn around and walk forward, then hang a left and walk up to the sink and look up at the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the chilled egg inside on the right side, then close the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled egg in the microwave.
